{"type":"text","timestamp":1775859726001,"sessionID":"ses_286863106ffeo6VSneMB4AUo03","part":{"id":"prt_d797cf007001ODmuhi3KaE883V","messageID":"msg_d797cde220017UI18BoAWCXYQX","sessionID":"ses_286863106ffeo6VSneMB4AUo03","type":"text","text":"Created tasks.md checklist for AR-016 (PicoD 文件管理 API) with 8 atomic, independently verifiable tasks following TDD pattern:\n\n**Tasks:**\n1. DELETE handler for file/directory deletion (with recursive support)\n2. PUT handler for directory creation (with recursive support)\n3. Metadata query parameter for GET /api/files/*path\n4. Recursive query parameter for GET /api/files (directory listing)\n5. File operation locks for concurrency control\n6. Enhanced path security with symlink resolution\n7. Comprehensive integration tests\n8. Final verification (coverage, linting, documentation)\n\nEach task follows Red-Green-Refactor cycle with failing tests → minimal implementation → verification → commit pattern.","time":{"start":1775859725999,"end":1775859725999}}}
